11. Re1 Bd7 12. Rc1 Rc8 13. Bb1 $5 {Of course, Whte has several other plans
like Re1-Ne5...or Qe2-Ne5...or Ne5 alone!} Be8 14. Ne5 Nxe5 15. dxe5 Nd7 16.
Bg3 $5 (16. Bxe7 Qxe7 17. Qc2 (17. Nf3 $16) 17... g6 18. Nf3 Nc5 19. Qd2 Kg7
20. Nd4 $16) 16... Qb6 17. Nb3 Bg5 18. Qd3 g6 19. Rcd1 Nc5 20. Nxc5 Rxc5 21. h4
