1007,1051,1084] A perfect game to show the problems that Black is facing in
these lines! ....He can never free himself by trading everything along the -f-
line ...and White keeps a very annoying initiative! ....In fact, i believe you
should learn the whole game by heart! ..and most likely it belongs to the...
CONCRETE THEORY game collection !} 1. d4 Nf6 2. Nf3 e6 3. Bg5 d5 4. Nbd2 Be7 5.
e3 O-O 6. Bd3 c5 7. c3 Nc6 (7... Qb6 $6 8. Rb1 Bd7 9. Qe2 (9. dxc5 Qxc5 10. e4)
