{perfect execution of the typical ideas in the e6-h6-g5 Tore ! ...a perfect
game by White!} 1. d4 Nf6 2. Nf3 e6 3. Bg5 h6 4. Bh4 d6 5. Nbd2 g5 6. Bg3 Nh5
7. e4 Nd7 8. Be2 (8. Bd3 $1 {this is possibly better than Be2..and this is
pretty much the only white inaccuracy in this game!!!}) 8... Bg7 9. c3 Qe7 10.
Nc4 b6 11. Nfd2 Nxg3 12. hxg3 Bb7 13. Ne3 O-O-O 14. a4 Rhf8 15. a5 Nb8 16. axb6
axb6 17. Qc2 Qd7 18. Bg4 Rh8 19. Ndc4 Rde8 1-0

